<i>Posted by SisterLi on 04-27-2001 11:38 PM:</i>

<p><b><img src="images/icons/icon5.gif" alt="Question" width="15" height="15" border="0"> Only drops from Garou?</b></p>

<p>Voocha - what is the basis for your claim that the spell only drops off Garou?  The spell location list states that it also drops off Guardian Wurms in GD, and one other mob besides Garou.  This would seem to suggest that at least some shaman have found the spell on other mobs.  I cannot speak for myself on this issue because I also purchased mine.<br>
<br>
I did spend several days camping for Garou, for a few hours at a time.  We never even saw him, and we had a tracker on board.  We killed cougars and snow dervishes, but never did discover what his place holder was.  Of course, mileage may vary.<br>
<br>
Your group would do well in GD.  You may want to consider moving them there if you go a few and do not spot the elusive Garou.<br>
