<p>Looted my copy on our very first Flying Monkey kill - lucky bastard that I am.  <img src="images/smilies/smile.gif" border="0" alt=""><br>
<br>
Bring a group of 50+ there to help with the break and camp 'em all day long for every level 39 spell.  (Yes -EVERY.)  Trouble is the cave is bugged and they fall below the world so be prepared to get a total wipeout on break - and have to petition to get those monkies killed by a GM.  (We had a full group of 55+ wiped out in 30 seconds.  10+ simultaneous rains will do that to you...)<br>
